   Scenario   *****   activate the ecommerce facility    *****
   Given      the user is on the home page
   When       the user click on activate the ecommerce facility
   Then       the ecommerce facility should be activated
   
   
   
   
   Scenario   *****   upgrade accounting   ******
   Given      the user is on homepage
   When       the user click on upgrade accounting
   Then       the accounting facility should be activated
   
   
   
   Scenario   *****    all the services currently running    ******
   Given      the user is on the homepage
   When       the user click on all the services currently running
   Then       all the services currently running are shown
